full_text: NO. 1741361 EMBLEM STAMPS R.1464299 THE SUBSCRIBED CHIEF OF THE CIVIL REGISTER, E R T I THAT AT PAGE 150 OF THE BOOK OF RECORDS OF BIRTHS THAT THIS OFFICE TOOK IN THE YEAR OF 1914 AT PAGE NO 30, IS FOUND THE RECORD THAT LITERALLY SAYS: " PA. NO. 67 MUNICIPAL MAYORS OFFICE: ILOBASCO, FEBRAURY TWELVE OF ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED AND FOURTEEN.- CANDELARIA ANGEL, FEMALE, LEGITIMATE DAUGHTER OF ANGEL AND JUANA ESTER GOMEZ, ORIGINARY FROM THIS DOMICILE, BORN THE TWO OF THE CURRENT MONTH AT THE TWO OF THE MORNING IN THE VALLEY OF SAN JOSE OF THIS JURISDICTION. GAVE THE DATA THE SAME FATHER AND DID NOT SIGN, FOR NOT KNOWING HOW BUT WAS DONE AT HIS PETITION BY WHOM APPEARES ELOFOLDO LOPEZ/VICENTE CASTILLO/ RUBEN MARTINEZ SCTRY. 11 RUBRICS."- IS CONFORMING WITH ITS ORIGINAL WITH WHICH IT WAS COMPULSED: AND FOR THE USES THAT MAY BE CONVENINET FOR THE INTERESTED, THE PRESENT IS EXPEDITED IN THE OFFICE OF THE CIVIL REGISTER OF THE MUNICIPAL MAYORS OFFICE OF ILOBASCO, AT TWENTY SEVEN OF JANUARY OF ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED AND EIGHTY TTWO AMMENDED- THAT -VALUES. SIGNATURE AND RUBBER STAMP. COMPULSED BY NAME AND SIGGNATURE AND TITLE. THIS IS A TRANSLATION FROM THE SPANISH LANGUAGE INTO THE ENGLISH LANGUAGE, DONE TO THE BEST OF MY KNWOLEDGE, I CERTIFY THAT I HAVE NOT CHANGE, ADDED, DELETED OR OMITTED ANY WORDS . C NOHEMI T RUEDA SUBSCRIBED AND SWORN TO BEFORE ME ON THIS 3RD DAY OF JUNE OF 1987. IN THE CITY OF SAN FERNANDO, CALIFORNIA. 91340. MAURO FRANK GUTIERREZ / NOTARY PUBLIC. OFFICIAL SEAL MAURO FRANK GUTIERREZ Notary Public-California LOS ANGELES COUNTY My Comm. Exp. Oct. 25. 1989
